profile:
Servicing Simcoe Country and Muskoka. We control ALL pest insects (ants, wasps, spiders etc.), rodents (beaver, mice, squirrels etc.), wildlife (bats, raccoons, skunks, moles etc), and birds (starlings, pigeons etc.)
We also identify and seal openings used by pests and clean up any mess they have left behind.
name: Robertson's Wildlife And Pest Control
